  "text": "Age estimation of Tanuki haplogroup and selection on Tanuki haplogroup: We conducted several age estimates in this paper. First, we used the simple formula detailed (15) in [CITATION_1] and estimated the expected time for the Tanuki haplogroup to reach the current frequency in East Asia and Europe under neutrality.",
